This is the Debian GNU/Linux `doc-debian' package. It provides various
important documentation describing Debian.

This package was first put together by Sven Rudolph, and later maintained
by Santiago Vila. Current maintainer is Josip Rodin <jrodin@jagor.srce.hr>.

